metadata.name: CALM IN THE CHAOS BAG #2
metadata.description:
CALM IN THE CHAOS BAG


Introducing the ‘Calm In The Chaos Bag,’ a special edition collaboration piece brought to you by NFSHE x Stacy Igel. Inspired by Igel’s new book ‘Embracing The Calm In The Chaos’ this bag is a celebration of women and entrepreneurs everywhere. As the founders behind this collaboration know, building a brand means embracing uncertainty, determination, and creativity. Handmade in New York City, the tote bag has an open design, top handles, and an exterior pocket with a distinct number embroidered on the top left corner, indicating the bag's production order and ensuring that each piece is one-of-a-kind. 


Perks & Utility:


TOTE BAG

Receive the physical ‘Calm In The Chaos Bag’ with the ‘Embracing The Calm In The Chaos’ book by Stacy Igel

- Bag Features: handmade, 100% organic cotton canvas, webbing straps, 1 exterior pocket, open top, embroidery of the NFSHE logo, Stacy Igel's 'Embracing The Calm In The Chaos' book title, and unique bag number

- Dimensions:  8.5in W x 2.25in D x 9.25in H, 4.5in strap drop


RARITY

Each ‘Calm In The Chaos Bag’ is uniquely numbered by production order


COMMUNITY

Gain entry to the NFSHE holder community



Policy:

All sales are final. Only primary sales are eligible for the physical product
